## 1. Strategic context

krishraja.com is the personal brand hub for Krish Raja. Its job, from now on, is one thing:

**Make Krish look like the most credible operator-advisor in the AI commercialization space, then hand serious buyers to Mindmaker.**

That's it. Not a resumé. Not a cohort catalog. Not a portfolio gallery. A conversion asset for Mindmaker and Techonomic, framed around a single claim: *Krish runs an autonomous AI business and helps companies commercialize theirs.*

### The positioning shift

**From:** "AI Revenue Leader | 16 Years Scaling Businesses" (reads as resumé)
**To:** "Operator-advisor running an agentic AI business" (reads as differentiated practitioner)

The 16 years of commercial track record do not disappear. They become **credentials for the advisor, not the identity.**

### What this site is NOT

- A career profile looking for inbound recruiter interest
- A comprehensive directory of every venture or project
- A cohort / course catalog (Mindmaker owns this)
- A blog (Techonomic owns this)
- A portfolio gallery of 11 ventures (trim to 6)

