## 15. Decision log

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
| Reposition from "AI Revenue Leader" to "Operator-advisor" | Current positioning reads like resumé; damages Mindmaker conversion when enterprise buyers google Krish |
| Keep as single page | Complexity doesn't serve a personal bio; single-page forces focus |
| Lead with "How I operate," demote ProofPoints | Operator narrative is the differentiator; 16 years of commercial track record is credential for the operator, not the other way around |
| Flip the "18 People → 14 Agents" card | One card that narrates the career arc in a single line; highest-leverage copy change |
| Trim portfolio from 11 to 6 ventures | More reads as scattered; fewer reads as focused |
| Delete the 5-offer LearnWithMe; replace with 3-card WorkWithMe | Current cohort catalog competes with Mindmaker; better to route cleanly |
